        "body": "Hey Vince, \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI can definitely help troubleshoot that. When you're testing, be sure to use a new private browsing session each time, since Locksmith will remember your previous access level in the browser. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIf your'e using a VPN to test, always try using a new private session: \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.locksmith.guide/tutorials/more/how-to-use-a-private-browsing-session\"\u003ehttps://www.locksmith.guide/tutorials/more/how-to-use-a-private-browsing-session\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI wasn't able to find a Shopify store using your email address. Can you send me the .myshopify.com url for your shop?\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eCheers!\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eKen\u003cbr /\u003e",
