        "body": "\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003eI reached out to Shopify and they suggested your app\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e--\u003cspan style=\"color:#374151;font-family:Inter, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;background-color:#FFF;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;float:none;\"\u003eTo restrict your Shopify store to only Canadian visitors, Shopify doesn't offer a direct feature. However, you can explore third-party apps like\u003cspan\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cem style=\"color:#374151;font-family:Inter, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;background-color:#FFF;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;border:0px solid #e5e7eb;\"\u003eLocksmith\u003c/em\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:#374151;font-family:Inter, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;background-color:#FFF;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;float:none;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c/span\u003efor geo-restrictions.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003eI am in Canada , and only advertise to Canada , BUT i want to be able to give access to IP from USA and INdia developers to work on the site\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003ehere is whats happening to my site\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin:0;padding:0;font-family:arial;font-size:14pt;\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/inline/103446/03b70b4b6565ea2e470f83966f6e0a5ffddc4d4b/876d3446cba68a637403aec9c6f3d880801e83b3/img-0.png\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
